Discount Investment to Sell Shufersal for 2.42 Billion Shekels

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-10-16T06:35:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/discount-investment-to-sell-shufersal-for-2-42-billion-shekels.html
Discount Investment Corp. (DISI)  signed a
memorandum of understanding to sell its 46 percent stake in
 Shufersal Ltd. (SAE)  for 24.18 shekels a share, or 2.42 billion
shekels. Discount will sell the holding in  Israel ’s biggest
supermarket chain to Isralom Properties Ltd. and  England ’s Noe
family, according to a statement filed with the Tel Aviv Stock
Exchange on Oct. 14.  TASE Filings:  http://maya.tase.co.il/bursa/indextoday.htm   To contact the reporter on this story:
